originalText.text: Worse Service Ever- Nothing was booked correctly. I called with my company's BTA and when I got to the airport my car was not reserved correctly and I had to use my own personal credit card. I arrived at the hotel and had to pay out of pocket for the room as well becuase the BTA again was not on the reservation as it should have been. And to top if off I called customer service about the $700 charges on my cc and they spoke to me as if this was my fault that their agent screwed up everything. Companies steer clear and use another service, you do not want your executives going out of town and potentially not having a place to stay or a car to drive.
